Class NscCoreController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.acordier.nsc.controller.NscCoreController

  • public class NscCoreController
extends java.lang.Object
    ModelController owns an instance of MidiInstrument and is responsible to execute control request addressed by any individual control controller used by the view.

    acordier
